phrases: These the massive, hostile creatures who traverse space-time, known as DRAGON.
To protect human territory by intercepting and destroying them
is the task of the Norma at Arzenal.
We Norma are allowed to live in this world only as weapons that kill DRAGONs.
Let us not forget that as we give our all to fight them.
We have a lot of learning and training to do.
The Empire of Misurugi will send a release order for me soon.
And once you are ready, you will serve the humans as riders and mechanics.
Officer, we are done educating Ange.
We are assigning her to First Troop today.
That will be your purpose in life.
So that is the princess everyone is talking about.
You do not care as long it is somebody new, right?
take it easy with the skinship.
We get complaints about how hard you massage the newcomers.
I will be careful, Deputy Chief.
She is an older newcomer, but be nice to her, you two.
Hey, Salia, time for a quiz!
Who is going to die first?
It is our job to teach them so they will not die.
Getting along well today, too, I see.
And this is our assault soldier, Vivian.
We Norma are treated as things.
Yep, we are all Norma, just like you.
We will be good friends, okay?
I am the Empire of Misurugi's First Princess, Angelise Ikaruga Misurugi.
But you cannot use Mana, right?
Th-The Light of Mana just does not reach this far.
In the State, I assure you...
You brought us a crazy one!
She is not even aware of her situation.
So the defect is being condescending?
Come on, people, let us leave it there.
We need to smack the delusion out of ugly bitches like her.
You are always too soft, Ersha.
Salia, you take care of her.
That is why the newcomers always act tough.
Be nice to the promising newcomer, everyone.
All right, we are starting training.
We will be doing long-range attack patterns.
Salia, Hilda, Vivian, you are training the newcomer.
No one may give orders to royalty.
Here, your superiors' orders are absolute.
That is too scandalous for me.
Oh, that is the previous owner.
I-I am wearing a dead person's clothes?
If you want a new one, you will have to buy it yourself.
I would rather be naked than wear that.
You would rather be naked, would not you?
They are just like the Institute said.
How barbaric and crude and violent!
You have never put your own clothes on before?
Man, you are worse than a kid.
My, my, you are swollen red.
The outside bolts are all wrecked.
I will replace them with ones from the Empire of Misurugi.
It will cost a bit more, though.
Could not you be a bit more careful with it?
It is not as durable as you are.
Is it really a good idea to put her in First Troop?
I do not expect you to be able to do this on your first try.
First, you need to get a good feel for flying.
Just what do you expect me to do?
Do not let go of the controls.
Real battle is worse than this.
You are going to hit the ground.
What is up with this kid?
She did not wet herself on her first simulation.
Ah, my first time was, well...
You can have it to yourself until we have new soldiers.
Buy what you need with this.
Roll call is at 5 tomorrow morning.
Her basic fitness, her reflexes, her combat adaptability,
She is above average in all areas.
I want to keep some for later.
You are such a kid, Coco.
You are not my older sister.
You are so good at everything, but you are picky about food.
You better eat up, or you will not be able to fight.
How can you eat that stuff?
Oh, is it not good enough for you, Burn Princess?
Here is a warning, Burn Princess.
This is not the world you came from.
You better figure that out quick, or you will die.
Oh, so you did not remember my name.
Come on, this is your chance to get to know her.
You are fast, and strong, and pretty.
I thought princesses were only in fairy tales.
Well, we are all new soldiers.
Let us stick together, okay, Ange?
Ask me if there is anything you do not know.
You can get more cash by making military gains.
So how did you shop outside?
I could have anything I wanted, and I could be anyone I wanted to.
There is no inequality, violence, or discrimination.
So there really is a magic nation.
Please, let me rest a little.
It is an invocation of my entitlements as royalty,
and a petition for my immediate release.
Please have this delivered to the heads of all states.
You still do not get it?
She is been poorly educated, Zola.
I will be borrowing the room.
You will not survive in the field
if you do not understand your situation.
I am returning to the Empire!
If I cannot tell you, I will have to teach your body.
Submit, and I will teach you pleasures you have never known.
That is how Norma have to be.
Lose an eye, lose an arm,
and the will to fight still runs through you.
You were sick of it, too, were not you?
This is the real deal, Ange.
Hauser, hurry up and load weapons.
You are on the one in the back, at the far left.
Singular opening expected at south by southeast, 4400.
No further details available, due to lack of response.
Para-mail First Troop, respond as appropriate upon contact.
Okay, little girls, it is your first battle.
You are providing support from the rear.
Stay calm and respond as necessary.
Do as you were taught, and you will not die.
Reactor internal temperature, two million Kelvins.
All First Troop units, ascend to engagement altitude.
How do you like the real Para-mail?
All right, all units prepare for battle.
We are almost at the battle zone!
My name is Angelise Ikaruga Misurugi.
I am returning to where I belong, in the Empire of Misurugi.
You will be shot if you disobey orders.
What are you talking about, Coco?
Take me to the magic country!
This week's story was terrible, too!
The food's awful, the rooms are dirty, I lost my first kiss...
Why do I have to go through all this?
Is not this a bishoujo robot anime?
